      <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions (as of 2022)</h2>

      <h3>Registration to the Conference</h3>
      <p>Refunds were accepted up to 7 days before the Conference.</p>

      <h3>Membership</h3>
      <p>Refunds were not offered, as membership was deemed to begin immediately.</p>

      <h3>Speakers &amp; Chairs withdrawal</h3>
      <p>
        Any last-minute withdrawal in the month before the Annual Conference was penalised with
        the suspension of participation rights for two years. Only exceptional circumstances were
        accepted as exemptions from this rule.
      </p>

